Pre-Game Insights: The series will start on May 22, 2024, in Leeds, with both teams aiming for momentum before the 2024 T20 World Cup
Miscellaneous Highlights: The series will be played at Headingley, Sophia Gardens, Kennington Oval, and Edgbaston, with England leading 7-4 in head-to-head records on home soil
Others: The last T20I match between the two teams was the 2022 World Cup final, won by England by five wickets
